      "text": "梦里归家那一扇灯",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 100.3,
      "time_str": "01:40.300",
      "text": "心中所属唯独你",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 102.92,
      "time_str": "01:42.920",
      "text": "不管分隔千里",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 104.67,
      "time_str": "01:44.670",
      "text": "痴心也在原地",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 107.44,
      "time_str": "01:47.440",
      "text": "旧日片段曾属你",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 110.26,
      "time_str": "01:50.260",
      "text": "紧紧拥抱不弃",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 112.08,
      "time_str": "01:52.080",
      "text": "终于再没逃避",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 114.76,
      "time_str": "01:54.760",
      "text": "若某天 风花雪月如泪",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 118.49,
      "time_str": "01:58.490",
      "text": "我等你 悲欢过后 如愿再聚",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
